## Flashing
Enter flash mode with the jumper on both mode mode pins and connect your serial-to-USB adapter to TX, RX, GND and 5V (use 3.3V pin from your adapter).

## Switching
Optionally, replacing 122 with 9 in the config above will allow use as a contact sensor instead of a button.
![](/assets/device_images/dohome_DIY_pins.webp)




